You should have the seperate PartyDetaildDTO one for Person and second for Organisation. It&#39;s unreadable if you used one DTO to create Party and Organization. Also the name should indicate that is person and that is organisation.

For example:
final PartyDetailsDTO personDTO = new PartyDetailsDTO();
final PartyDetailsDTO organisationDTO = new PartyDetailsDTO();
